parameters.name: Cert
parameters.description: The content of the certificate in the PEM format.

parameters.name: EncryptCert
parameters.description: The content of the encryption certificate in PEM format.

parameters.name: EncryptPrivateKey
parameters.description: The private key of the encryption certificate in the PEM format.

parameters.name: Key
parameters.description: The private key of the certificate in the PEM format.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description:
The name of the certificate. The name can be up to 64 characters in length, and can contain all types of characters, such as letters, digits, and underscores (\_).

>  The name must be unique within an Alibaba Cloud account.

parameters.name: SignCert
parameters.description: The content of the signing certificate in the PEM format.

parameters.name: SignPrivateKey
parameters.description: The private key of the signing certificate in the PEM format.
